episodes.title: Andrew has suffered the ULTIMATE humiliation but public may STILL bay for blood say royal experts
episodes.description:
In this clip from The Sun's Royal Exclusive our experts examine the public's reaction to Andrew Mountbatten Windsor's fall from grace.

03:12 - The reaction from the public
04:50 - Are there more allegations coming soon?
06:50 - Are there too many distractions between working Royals and Andrew?
